casebody.data:
HURON CITY COMPANY, Plaintiff/Counterdefendant-Appellee,
v.
Charles Abram PARCELLS, III and David Hamilton Parcells, Defendants/Counterplaintiffs/Third-Party Plaintiffs-Appellants,
and
Diane Stewart, Henry Stewart, Benjamin Stewart, Joshua Stewart, Walter Wagoner, Lynda Bogel, Jeff Parcells, Gretchen Madison, Steve Parcells, Nathan Parcells, and Matthew Parcells, Third-Party Defendants. SC: 157433
COA: 335978 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 2, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the February 8, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
